summary:
Recently graduated  I am looking for a full-time job as a communication specialist in the Netherlands, in the Utrecht Area.

My last experience was interning for DZK global, a group offering business tourism and event management services. I was in charge of all internal and external communication. In addition to setting up communication actions and designing communication supports, I also managed the different social media of the seven agencies on my own.

Throughout my 5 years of higher education, I learned the different fields of communication, such as the event or editorial part, online communication, intercultural communication, and so on. From theory to practice, I expanded my knowledge by redacting articles and social media content, organizing events from scratch, and creating visual content thanks to the Adobe Creative Suite. 

 Would you like to learn more?   

I look forward to hearing from you!
